# Title: Possible Impacket SecretDump Remote Activity
# Author: Samir Bousseaden, wagga
# Date: 2019-04-03
# Level: high
# Description: Detect AD credential dumping using impacket secretdump HKTL
# MITRE Tactic: Credential Access
# Tags: attack.credential-access, attack.t1003.002, attack.t1003.004, attack.t1003.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_impacket_secretdump.yml

EventID=5145 RelativeTargetName="*SYSTEM32\\*" RelativeTargetName="*.tmp*" ShareName="\\\\\*\\ADMIN$"